queries.query: SELECT mean("Get_Requests_persec") AS "gets" FROM ":db:".":rp:"."win_websvc" WHERE time > :dashboardTime: AND "host" = :host: GROUP BY time(:interval:)
SELECT mean("Post_Requests_persec") AS "posts" FROM ":db:".":rp:"."win_websvc" WHERE time > :dashboardTime: AND "host" = :host: GROUP BY time(:interval:)
SELECT mean("Current_Connections") AS "connections" FROM ":db:".":rp:"."win_websvc" WHERE time > :dashboardTime: AND "host" = :host: GROUP BY time(:interval:)
